# MarkdownUI Syntax Test

## Shorthand Syntax (Double Underscore)

__Primary Button|Click Me__

__Success Message|Operation completed successfully!__

__Large Header|Welcome to MarkdownUI__

__Striped Table|Name,Role|Alice,Developer|Bob,Designer__

## Longhand Syntax (Blockquote)

> Primary Button:
> Click Me

> Success Message:
> Operation completed successfully!

> Large Header:
> Welcome to MarkdownUI

> Striped Table:
> Name,Role
> Alice,Developer
> Bob,Designer

## Mixed Content

This is regular markdown **bold text** and *italic text*.

__Warning Message|Both syntaxes produce identical HTML!__

> Info Message:
> You can mix both formats in the same document!